        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "1. 用户登录",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            149,
            146,
            289,
            167
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "业主向经销商提供注册的邮箱及手机号码；",
        "bbox": [
            147,
            197,
            510,
            214
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "安装商新建场站，并为用户绑定设备；",
        "bbox": [
            147,
            219,
            477,
            235
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/459379793dce950011de11b5d9d290e98a223cb003bca7c1e1109b155779bca2.jpg",
        "image_caption": [
            ""
        ],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "bbox": [
            147,
            241,
            848,
            456
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "经销商在商储平台新建用户账号，并设定初始密码；",
        "bbox": [
            149,
            499,
            583,
            516
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/366ba6706fb9c7fa208dec8d9867eeb692595a22cec6c1600036cbbc0bb66392.jpg",
        "image_caption": [],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "bbox": [
            152,
            521,
            840,
            770
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "业主打开 APP 点击“登录”，首次登录，提示用户去重置密码；",
        "bbox": [
            146,
            781,
            673,
            797
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/7ebf4da35e7eee68fadee191a04b90ac5ae4a591ccbb8bff0b70fdc20ec8f2c9.jpg",
        "image_caption": [],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "bbox": [
            243,
            86,
            752,
            395
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "用户登录后，加载其场站设备信息。",
        "bbox": [
            149,
            404,
            458,
            420
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "2.服务商注册",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            147,
            482,
            304,
            505
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "打开 APP 点击“注册”，进入注册界面",
        "bbox": [
            147,
            533,
            490,
            550
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/353ac95fc38ba54defaf7e62dd741aee74eae9065787f0a48c144caed72c0f50.jpg",
        "image_caption": [],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "bbox": [
            383,
            554,
            615,
            862
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "选择根据自身定位，选择”经销商“或“安装商” ",
        "bbox": [
            147,
            870,
            569,
            887
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/9b078badc0808945f7b57d5b17c4eb45430b465413068b40ec43e0e447841643.jpg",
        "image_caption": [],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "bbox": [
            381,
            83,
            615,
            397
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "输入邮箱、营业证书、联系人、联系电话、公司名称、地址等信息（安装商需多提供电力施工资质，如电工证）",
        "bbox": [
            147,
            404,
            852,
            442
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/513554c2d8377f26307540f648f6467d87a19ba1058d2c37fffa1cc89a86ff62.jpg",
        "image_caption": [],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "bbox": [
            147,
            443,
            838,
            755
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "点击确认，注册成功。",
        "bbox": [
            149,
            763,
            352,
            780
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "3.创建场站（服务商）",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            149,
            878,
            393,
            900
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "登录 APP",
        "bbox": [
            149,
            91,
            255,
            105
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "打开 APP 点击场站按钮，点击场站列表右上角 $^ { \\prime \\prime } { } + ^ { \\prime \\prime }$ 按钮；",
        "bbox": [
            147,
            111,
            630,
            127
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/f764d926d064c59a61b858f76ac9d4b7ce63d8441f34ece62048f5c06f63d9e7.jpg",
        "image_caption": [],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "bbox": [
            262,
            130,
            736,
            439
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "扫描随箱资料上的 SN码标签或逆变器的 SN 码；",
        "bbox": [
            147,
            448,
            552,
            463
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "输入场站业的信息及邮箱、地址等信息，点击“下一步”；",
        "bbox": [
            147,
            469,
            635,
            486
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/e10205237bfbc83dc6943d931a22f699ae86b862e8e4912c08f9328df76bdce5.jpg",
        "image_caption": [],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "bbox": [
            147,
            507,
            836,
            818
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "显示当前站点已添加的设备，点击”下一步”;（如有没有检测与添加的设备，可先跳过）；",
        "bbox": [
            152,
            827,
            848,
            844
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "输入场站的参数，是否防逆流、工作模式，备电 SOC，充放电上下限及自定义并离网的设置，点击“下一步”；",
        "bbox": [
            146,
            848,
            852,
            885
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "自检，检测云平台连接、网络状态及直流侧、通讯及储能的状态，通过点击“下一步”；",
        "bbox": [
            144,
            891,
            850,
            908
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/977328f9478dec0bd57b4e7ae5909c3566d35ba8d01965c7d4512fc9932b0788.jpg",
        "image_caption": [],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "bbox": [
            181,
            85,
            820,
            395
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "确认设定的参数，建站成功。",
        "bbox": [
            149,
            405,
            406,
            420
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "4. 关机操作",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            147,
            466,
            285,
            488
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": " 设置（Setting) 场站设置（Plant Setup) 开关机 （Power on/off)",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            144,
            499,
            786,
            517
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/3de044f0d42b9d3b9ab507d499700342082889b143a6c98caa0c3203cb022b6a.jpg",
        "image_caption": [],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "bbox": [
            262,
            520,
            734,
            828
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "确认提示：",
        "bbox": [
            149,
            835,
            268,
            852
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "确定关机？系统将停止运行。点 确认系统安全停机流程：",
        "bbox": [
            147,
            857,
            546,
            896
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "先降功率 断并网 / 离网输出停止 $\\mathsf { P C S } $ 断开 DC 主继电器BMS 下电 系统进入待机（Standby）",
        "bbox": [
            216,
            87,
            569,
            148
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": " APP 显示：已关机（Off）、所有功率为 $\\ r _ { 0 } $ 关机完成。",
        "bbox": [
            147,
            152,
            675,
            171
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "5. 开机操作",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            147,
            215,
            285,
            236
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "设置（Setting) 场站设置（Plant Setup) 开关机（Power on/off)",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            149,
            247,
            746,
            266
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/19dc5922e22b8260b10e01c68b5d845779c172f7270c05dab289d44963c0c03b.jpg",
        "image_caption": [],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "bbox": [
            262,
            269,
            734,
            577
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "确认提示：",
        "bbox": [
            149,
            585,
            268,
            601
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "确定开机？系统将自检并启动。点 确认（Confirm）",
        "bbox": [
            206,
            606,
            663,
            624
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": " 系统自动执行：",
        "bbox": [
            149,
            627,
            310,
            644
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "BMS/ 电池自检 DC 预充、母线升压 →PCS 启动、并网 / 待机",
        "bbox": [
            166,
            649,
            791,
            667
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "$\\bullet$ 开机完成。",
        "bbox": [
            147,
            670,
            270,
            688
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "6. 充放电模式切换",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            149,
            770,
            363,
            791
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "在新建场站时已经选择一种运行模式（默认为自发自用模式）。",
        "bbox": [
            146,
            802,
            707,
            820
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": " 设置（Setting) 场站设置（Plant Setup) 运行模式（Power on/off)",
        "bbox": [
            141,
            824,
            786,
            843
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/e040d8ad37be3b8de511fa2f5e142ee56ddf933114bdd4a86b4ac8fef6b9aab5.jpg",
        "image_caption": [],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "bbox": [
            151,
            85,
            845,
            397
        ],
        "page_idx": 6
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": " 点击相应 AI模式、自发自用、按时间充放电的模式后的开关可进行切换。",
        "bbox": [
            147,
            403,
            828,
            420
        ],
        "page_idx": 6
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "$\\bullet$ 系统自动执行：",
        "bbox": [
            149,
            425,
            310,
            442
        ],
        "page_idx": 6
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "选择新的充放电模式后，云端校验后 设备停机/降载 状态自检 新策略加载 功率重启 反馈确认的完整流程",
        "bbox": [
            147,
            445,
            850,
            485
        ],
        "page_idx": 6
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "系统提供新充放电模式切换成功。",
        "bbox": [
            149,
            489,
            472,
            506
        ],
        "page_idx": 6
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "充放电模式设置",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            149,
            531,
            294,
            549
        ],
        "page_idx": 6
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "点击每个模式可对应设置每个模式的参数",
        "bbox": [
            184,
            552,
            551,
            570
        ],
        "page_idx": 6
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/eac64b75768b8281544905325244172dd4db492818980198f64d1f0ec75c6f00.jpg",
        "image_caption": [],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "bbox": [
            147,
            574,
            810,
            887
        ],
        "page_idx": 6
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "7.并离网-并转离（默认自动切换）",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            147,
            111,
            465,
            133
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": " APP 前置检查",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            147,
            165,
            304,
            183
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "电池 $50 C \\geq 5 0 \\%$ （建议 $\\ge 7 0 \\%$ ）无故障告警、系统正常负载功率 $\\leq$ 离网额定功率",
        "bbox": [
            179,
            187,
            440,
            247
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": " APP 操作",
        "bbox": [
            149,
            250,
            262,
            268
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "1. 进入设置（Setting) 场站设置（Plant Setup) 并离网（Grid connected andoff grid)",
        "bbox": [
            146,
            272,
            852,
            311
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/ff76b35899cfc49ca6c367b4b03da01a18f0ca5402ec3326ba3d862fc099b088.jpg",
        "image_caption": [],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "bbox": [
            383,
            315,
            611,
            623
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": " 点击 切换至离网 确认  \n 输入安全密码（如需）  \n$\\bullet$ 系统执行（后台自动）  \n 停止充放电 断开电网开关  \n PCS 进入离网 VF 模式（建立电压 / 频率）  \n 黑启动成功 带载运行  \n APP 状态显示：离网运行  \n$\\bullet$ 离网后注意仅备电回路供电不可超功率、不可并网观察 SOC，低电量自动停机",
        "bbox": [
            146,
            631,
            571,
            863
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "8.并离网-离转并（默认自动切换）",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            147,
            92,
            463,
            114
        ],
        "page_idx": 8
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "$\\bullet$ 检查条件  \n 电网已恢复、电压 / 频率正常  \n 无故障、电池电量充足  \n 负载不过载  \n$\\bullet$ APP 操作  \n 进入设置（Setting) 场站设置（Plant Setup) 并离网（Grid connected andoff grid)",
        "bbox": [
            149,
            122,
            855,
            272
        ],
        "page_idx": 8
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/4bd4bf7fe1eab04750cf01cf2c381657d7e0c02d8b3629b39e3bd092757117e6.jpg",
        "image_caption": [],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "bbox": [
            383,
            275,
            611,
            583
        ],
        "page_idx": 8
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "点击 切换至并网 确认 ",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            183,
            590,
            418,
            607
        ],
        "page_idx": 8
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "$\\bullet$ 系统执行（后台自动）",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            151,
            612,
            376,
            629
        ],
        "page_idx": 8
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "离网停机 检测电网  \n锁相（电压 / 频率 / 相位同步）  \n闭合并网开关 并网运行  \nAPP 状态：并网运行",
        "bbox": [
            181,
            633,
            475,
            715
        ],
        "page_idx": 8
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "9.系统自检",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            147,
            821,
            272,
            843
        ],
        "page_idx": 8
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/79880ed3097fb99bdfdf091106ff294a2b59aa13c1c1b1a1d215fc02771d936c.jpg",
        "image_caption": [],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "bbox": [
            151,
            85,
            847,
            395
        ],
        "page_idx": 9
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "自检结果：通过 / 异常",
        "bbox": [
            149,
            403,
            393,
            420
        ],
        "page_idx": 9
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "检测项：电池系统（BMS）检测、逆变器（PCS）检测、电网与电气安全检测、系统与通信检测",
        "bbox": [
            151,
            426,
            852,
            463
        ],
        "page_idx": 9
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "自检完成后返回各模块状态结果，失败则提示用户重新自检或反馈给经销商。",
        "bbox": [
            149,
            469,
            742,
            485
        ],
        "page_idx": 9
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": " APP 操作",
        "bbox": [
            149,
            489,
            262,
            506
        ],
        "page_idx": 9
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "进入设置（Setting) 场站设置（Plant Setup) 自检（Self Inspection)",
        "bbox": [
            168,
            510,
            825,
            527
        ],
        "page_idx": 9
    },
    {
